    <!-- Big Agent App box -->
    <mxCell id="b4" value="&lt;b&gt;Teams Agent App&lt;/b&gt;  (aiohttp · Python)&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;/api/messages — Teams bot endpoint&lt;br&gt;/webhook — Graph notifications&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;pipeline.run():&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;• Fetch VTT via Graph API&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;• Parse transcript (VTT → text)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;• Gemini 1.5 Flash → insights&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;• POST results to Monday.com"
